{"tid":497701,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［求貓奴］點樣解決小貓係被度柯尿","createTime":"2017-12-13T05:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T10:16:27.000Z","uid":78668,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"745ac937d3329187a374d9002a21f2f0c743fb15","tid":497701,"uid":78668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:02:37.000Z","msg":"小貓岩岩2個月大 拎番屋企個幾禮拜<br />\n其實佢係識用貓砂 <br />\n平日朝早晏就都會識去貓砂柯<br />\n但唯獨一到夜晚就好鍾意係我張被上邊屙尿<br />\n已經日日洗被 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2張被輪住都係咁夜晚接近想瞓覺嘅時候就會屙<br />\n試過日頭將張被收埋 到瞓覺先開返張被<br />\n點知一開出嚟就上去柯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求各位貓奴求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebeba36bd9d52e2ee21adcc5dae6b749468e5b17","tid":497701,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"冇記錯，有啲驅貓狗噴霧<br />\n噴落床試下"},{"pid":"5b21984a0494286307b78d9e643921d87bc464db","tid":497701,"uid":134323,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"自己柯一督落去先，<br />\n隻貓會知個地盤俾人霸左去第二度柯"},{"pid":"3fd4862b241a36687e9c42863d9f606a0f1c9af9","tid":497701,"uid":78668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇記錯，有啲驅貓狗噴霧<br />\n噴落床試下</blockquote><br />\n噴落自己張被我日日吸住有無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58e25e7a558420bbd86dc96857bf75343dd3e14","tid":497701,"uid":85427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:14:01.000Z","msg":"唔俾佢入房咪得。。不嬲養到熟先入得房"},{"pid":"2a125c57aa7d8b3dbd41b9374a40af2d7da55b8a","tid":497701,"uid":78668,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔俾佢